c: 4
v: 127
t: "Ne bakhurebanga okhulondokhana nende amakhuwa kabakhasi, boola mbu; “Nyasaye yetsa okhubaboolela bulaano buri, nende kamusomelungwa mushitabu aka Abana abafwilwa nende Abakhasi balia bamwalayelisinjia ebia balachilwa, ne mwikomba okhubateshia, nende balia 4. abateshele mubana. Ne mbu mukholele Abana abafwila obwatoto. Ne kamukhola mumalayi Nyasaye akamanyile muno"